      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUN ROLEX (8) has been in sparkling form scoring back to back wins, the latest by 3.5 lengths (17.44) over 300m at this track. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. In top form and looks a key chance again. SHE'S A PANAMA (1) was a last-start winner from the inside at this track and distance (17.58), scoring by 2.25 lengths. Expected to be in the finish. ZIPPING GIDEY (5) jumped from box 7 last time and ran away with an impressive win scoring by 6 lengths at this track in a handy 17.39. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Solid formlines coming through her last run. One of the leading chances again. BARGAIN BETTY (2) is in form and worth thought again.",
